wdi-BN.CAB.XOKA.CD.def: Current account balance is the sum of net exports of goods and services, net primary income, and net secondary income. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BN.CAB.XOKA.CD.name: Current account balance
wdi-BN.CAB.XOKA.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
